<L>__{interior elevator night}
<A>__{the doors open, wilson pushes chance into the elevator. as wilson pushes a button and the doors close on them, a strange look comes over chance's face.}
<C>__{chance}
<P>__{(looks to wilson)}
<D>__{... i've never been in one of these.}
<A>__{wilson thinks that chance is talking about the wheelchair.}
<C>__{wilson}
<D>__{it's one of mr. rand's. since he's been ill...}
<A>__{chance looks around the elevator.}
<C>__{chance}
<D>__{does it have a television?}
